getting the question correct correlates&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:53.200 --> 00:01:59.120
positively or negatively with performing&nbsp;
well on the exam overall. In other words&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:59.120 --> 00:02:04.960
if students scored well on the exam as a&nbsp;
whole they should on average score well&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:04.960 --> 00:02:10.240
on the item students who performed&nbsp;
